<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10272221>
    dc:description "Figs 25–32. Dichagyris spp. 25–26 = D. turana turana (Staudinger, 1892): 25 = male, Kirghisia, Issyk-Kul, 26 = female, Uzbekistan, Kyzyl-Kum. 27–28 = D. turana cisiliensis ssp. n., Kazakhstan, Chu-Ili Mts: 27 = holotype, male, 28 = paratype, male. 29–30 = D. furiosa furiosa (Bang-Haas, 1912), Tadjikistan, Peter the Great Mts, Garm: 29 = lectotype, male, 30 = paralectotype, male. 31–32 = D. furiosa griseoerythra ssp. n., Kirghisia, Naryn region, Sarykam-" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10272221/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10272239>
    dc:description "Figs 56–58. Male genitalia of Dichagyris spp. 56–57 = D. turana cisiliensis ssp. n., Kazakhstan, Chu Ili Mts: 56 = paratype, slide No.: VZ9957m; 57 = paratype, slide No.: VZ10006m. 58 = D. furiosa furiosa (Bang-Haas, 1912), lectotype, Tadjikistan, Peter the Great Mts, Garm, slide No.: Boursin MB360m" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10272239/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

