    dc:description "Figs 59–61. Male genitalia of Dichagyris furiosa sspp. 59 = D. furiosa furiosa (Bang-Haas, 1912), Tadjikistan, Alai range, slide No.: VZ11989m. 60–61 = D. furiosa griseoerythra ssp. n.," ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10272243/files/figure.png" ;
