<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10272257>
    dc:description "Figs 74–76. Female genitalia of Dichagyris spp. 74 = D. turana cisiliensis ssp. n., paratype, Kazakhstan, Chu Ili Mts, slide No.: VZ9962f. 75–76 = D. furiosa furiosa (Bang-Haas, 1912):" ;
